your coworkers or possibly other external partners.

15
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:45,130
Recommendation.

16
00:00:45,130 --> 00:00:47,840
Adopt your workflow within your control.

17
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:51,170
You will likely not be successful by enlarging the workflow value

18
00:00:51,170 --> 00:00:54,150
stream to areas where you cannot control the work,

19
00:00:54,150 --> 00:00:57,110
cannot control someone else's team, their resources,

