Here are the key points of value stream endpoints.

40
00:01:55,990 --> 00:01:57,360
By defining boundaries,

41
00:01:57,360 --> 00:02:00,040
you are asking your team to adopt limiting work in

42
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:02,680
progress only for your value stream.

43
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:06,080
You can't ask your upstream or downstream partners to do that.

44
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:10,240
