45
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,890
Again, you don't need to tell them that you're using Kanban,

46
00:02:12,890 --> 00:02:16,190
but you are asking them to provide you what you need

47
00:02:16,190 --> 00:02:19,680
that would support a pull system, and on the other end,

48
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:24,640
a way to deliver what you have produced.

