52
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:38,640
It allows you to visualize and bound your process, your value stream.

53
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:42,550
It helps you optimize the way you deliver value to your customers.

54
00:02:42,550 --> 00:02:45,690
So designing your value stream in conjunction with determining those

55
